      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted enthusiast's example, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with high-pressure Double VANOS and individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring precise power delivery to the rear wheels. The chassis has been maintained with a focus on subframe integrity and refreshed bushings to preserve its celebrated handling dynamics. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and a cooling system refresh. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the engine's compression remains strong and the gear shifts are crisp, offering a visceral, high-RPM driving experience.",
