      "description": "Available is a well-sorted E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission shifts crisply, paired with the factory M Variable Differential Lock for precise torque distribution. The suspension has been enhanced with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, maintaining the chassis's legendary communicative feedback. While the exterior reflects honest mileage, the mechanical vitals\u2014including recent valve clearances and Rod Bearing service\u2014are optimized for performance longevity. A true driver\u2019s specification prioritized for mechanical excellence.",
